{"tid":494531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"17-18 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽半程總結 朱千雪6分領放勇奪冬季冠軍","createTime":"2017-12-09T16:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T11:38:37.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"873619bee5aaa587752582ad15c953471a869b2a","tid":494531,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TmG58Bg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTmG58Bg.png&h=d5694f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首循環總結:<br />\n榜首朱千雪以45分既6分差距領導群芳奪冬季半程冠軍<br />\n而升班馬之中數苟芸慧成績最標青,力壓謝安琪呢位傳統勁女排喺聯賽榜前三位<br />\n護級形勢方面,林嘉欣-麥明詩-趙慧珊@SG分別得9分,7分同6分,理論上都仲有護級成功同降班既機會<br />\n至於榜尾簡淑兒...15戰全敗狂失764分,僅入168分,相信都死左9成以上架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另附半季橫向聯賽排名走勢表,多謝呢半季以黎一直或者間唔中都有入過黎參與過下既巴打既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HQtvNGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHQtvNGc.png&h=1d7a93b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bbd6c2297e54787793c31b3f2653d442f3cc8a6","tid":494531,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1340992a3cf5714e075afa42b3762cd21bd0a94","tid":494531,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"簡淑兒係唔係會被踢出所有聯賽?"},{"pid":"7a03cad2f9cafe3e1a0541ac210305c9d92e61ff","tid":494531,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"<block